  <title>Harry Potter actor Robert Hardy dead at 91</title>
  <content>
London: British actor Robert Hardy, who played Minister For Magic, Cornelius Fudge in the Harry Potter films, has died at the age of 91.
Hardy was also known for playing Siegfried Farnon in BBC series All Creatures Great and Small.Photo: Fairfax Media
A statement from his family says: "It is with great sadness that the family of Robert Hardy CBE today announced his death, following a tremendous life: a giant career in theatre, television and film spanning more than 70 years."
PA
